                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           <locus target="#4ra">4ra, l. 1</locus> በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡
                           ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ተአምር፡ ዘይትነበብ፡ እምቅድመ፡ ያንብቡ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ሥርዓት፡
                           ዘወጽአ፡ እምንበረ፡ ማርቆስ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ እመካነ፡ መዓልቃ፡ ዘምስር፡ ዘአንበሩ፡ መምህራን፡ መጋብያነ፡ ምሥጢር፡ ርቱዓነ፡
                           ሃይማኖት።<foreign xml:lang="en">In
                              the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit, One God.
                              This book of miracles that is read before the Miracles of Our Lady Mary.
                              This book of rules that came from the seat of Mark the Apostle, from the
                              church of Mäʿalqa (al-Muʿallaqah) of Mǝsr (i.e. Cairo), which the
                              doctors, glorious patriarchs, treasurers of the mystery, the righteous
                              had laid up (there).</foreign>
                        </incipit>
