                        wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... "I worship Thee..." (fols. 13rb-14rb)&#xD; I-4a) Taʾammǝra
                        Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 1 miracle (fols. 14rb-15vb)</summary>
                     <msItem xml:id="p2_i1">
                        <locus from="11r" to="15v"></locus>
